<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: '#4f46e5',
                        secondary: '#7c3aed',
                        accent: '#c084fc',
                        dark: '#111827'
                    },
                    fontFamily: {
                        sans: ['Inter', 'sans-serif']
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 font-sans">
    <nav class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200 sticky top-0 z-30">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 py-4">
            <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                <a class="flex items-center gap-2 text-primary font-bold text-xl" href="#">
                    <i class="fas fa-heartbeat text-2xl"></i> MMU Hospital
                </a>
                <div>
                    <a class="bg-primary hover:bg-indigo-600 text-white font-medium px-5 py-2 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-indigo-200" href="/login">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt mr-2"></i>Login
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="relative overflow-hidden py-32 lg:py-40">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-600 via-primary to-purple-700 opacity-90"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1576091160550-2173dba999ef?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1470&q=80')] bg-no-repeat bg-cover mix-blend-overlay opacity-20"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10">
            <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">Blockchain-Based Medical Records Management</h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-indigo-100 mb-10">Secure, Transparent, and Immutable Healthcare Data</p>
                <a href="/login" class="inline-block bg-white text-primary font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-lg shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-1">
                    Get Started <i class="fas fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 1440 320" class="text-slate-50 fill-current">
                <path d="M0,128L80,144C160,160,320,192,480,186.7C640,181,800,139,960,138.7C1120,139,1280,181,1360,202.7L1440,224L1440,320L1360,320C1280,320,1120,320,960,320C800,320,640,320,480,320C320,320,160,320,80,320L0,320Z"></path>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-20 container mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-4">Why Choose MMU Hospital?</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">MMU Hospital uses blockchain technology to create a secure, transparent, and efficient healthcare data management system. Our platform helps healthcare providers maintain accurate records while giving patients control over their medical information.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-dark">Advanced Security</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">All medical records are encrypted and stored securely on the blockchain, ensuring data integrity and privacy for patients and healthcare providers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-users-cog text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-dark">Role-Based Access</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Different roles (admin, doctor, patient) have specific permissions to maintain privacy and data protection while ensuring appropriate access.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-2 overflow-hidden group">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-500 to-purple-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 text-primary mb-6 group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-database text-2xl"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3 text-dark">Immutable Records</h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600">Medical records stored on the blockchain cannot be altered or deleted, ensuring a complete and accurate medical history for better healthcare.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-50 to-purple-50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-6">Transforming Healthcare Data Management</h2>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 mb-8">MMU Hospital uses blockchain technology to create a secure, transparent, and efficient healthcare data management system. Our platform helps healthcare providers maintain accurate records while giving patients control over their medical information.</p>
                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-medium text-dark">Enhanced Data Security</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Protected by advanced cryptographic methods</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-medium text-dark">Interoperability</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Seamless integration with existing healthcare systems</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                <i class="fas fa-check text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h4 class="font-medium text-dark">Transparent Access Logs</h4>
                                <p class="text-sm text-slate-600">Complete record of who accessed what and when</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="md:w-1/2">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1586773860418-d37222d8fce3?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1473&q=80" alt="Medical Technology" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="bg-dark text-white pt-16 pb-8">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mb-12">
                <div>
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> MMU Hospital
                    </h4>
                    <p class="text-slate-400">Secure blockchain solutions for healthcare data management.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold mb-6 text-indigo-300">Quick Links</h5>
                    <ul class="space-y-3">
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">Home</a></li>
                        <li><a href="#" class="text-slate-400 hover:text-white transition-colors">About Us</a></li>
